des: The Highway is your Country Powerhouse! This station covers Ashe, Watauga, Avery, Wilkes, TN counties and beyond. Be sure to listen live in the mornings to JB (Jeff Brown) from 6am-10am, afternoons with Dave Thomas from 3pm-7pm, and The Lia Show from 7pm-midnight! You can also follow along, all day, on the Highway Facebook and Instagram pages! Stay tuned in for weekly ticket giveaways to your favorite events, artist’s shows and NASCAR.
